Package model

Class LevelModel

java.lang.Object
model.LevelModel
public class LevelModel
extends java.lang.Object
The LevelModel class creates levels for the Game. I separated these methods from the WallController class as the Game should not be responsible for creating the levels. This class contains simple implementations of next level as well.
